	   <tr><td colspan=2>Aye... and note that while Charmies are quite risky to use as they tend to turn on you (anything blue or better will within a short amount of time (at least when under 150 cha)) they are severely more effective in that short term than your own pet;&nbsp;&nbsp;They hit significantly harder, and if you pick good targets, can cast, strike, and use skills not typical of our happy prancing sword and shield.<br>&nbsp;<br>&lt;&lt; Pryss Valjurai &gt;&gt;</td></tr>
