	   <tr><td colspan=2>That's the only time I use Charm, for excessive Crowd Control.&nbsp;&nbsp;Not always preferable to keep AE mezzing a crowd of 5 or more, often in this crowd one resists (in addition to the one your group wakes by whacking it), so charm that one and /assist your tank and drop them faster.  I much prefer to be able to single-mez, at my level I use Enthrall which lasts twice as long as AE mez.<br>Charm is also decent if you have a stupid group that wakes up your mezzed mobs.  Then charm takes away that option.  :P<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
